org.wicketstuff.select2

Class ApplicationSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wicketstuff.select2.ApplicationSettings

  • public class ApplicationSettings
extends Object
    Application-wide settings that apply to all Select2 components. The settings object is retreived via the static get() method and is usually configured in the WebApplication.init() method.
    Author:
    igor
